{"tid":1288771,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"7月7或成反送中最大突破點","createTime":"2019-07-05T18:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T19:10:48.000Z","uid":259980,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"90111c80151cded243cb215aa6fdcab84a9576ee","tid":1288771,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:36:14.000Z","msg":"好多問題唔明想問下大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n77原意係向內地人宣傳反送中<br />\n<br />\n但內地人一向唔推崇民主就未必有興趣嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係如果有人用咗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">武漢示威</span></span>嚟做宣傳<br />\n<br />\n嗌住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">聲援武漢</span></span><br />\n播晒片咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話佢係內地版反送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再宣傳埋反送中<br />\n<br />\n共產黨會唔會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">好驚架</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果同時有連登仔去<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">內地論壇/聊天軟件</span></span>行下<br />\n<br />\n用<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">支持藍絲嘅方式</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n去支援武漢<br />\n順便將佢同反送中綁埋一齊#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#<br />\n<br />\n武漢單野會唔會變到超級大件事架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知道如果上面嘅事發生咗<br />\n遊行焦點可能會模糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但覺得<br />\n既然77最終目的係<br />\n宣傳內地人去震動中央<br />\n＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點都好<br />\n77大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fedc5845fe79c9bf40abb1d05ecbd08054be1d16","tid":1288771,"uid":156592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:37:27.000Z","msg":"【重要】七七遊行同airdrop嘅文宣方向建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1286038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1286038</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0aeea025d8afbdd4d2ebb5a7555d40536eea15a0","tid":1288771,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:45:14.000Z","msg":"個人認為<br />\n如果69、616、71咁多次遊行<br />\n抗議反送中都無咩效果<br />\n其實應該要變招<br />\n好似攬炒巴請求剝奪官員權利嚟抗議反送中咁<br />\n點解唔試下搞到中央大頭佛嚟反送中<br />\n唔好因為係內地人嘅遊行就好反感<br />\n佢地都係抗爭緊<br />\n雖然唔係為民主係為環境<br />\n但至少有反抗嘅人<br />\n可以利用<br />\n就可以一試<br />\nbe water"},{"pid":"d4da2890d8b587c7f0845264818030f0cff76a63","tid":1288771,"uid":76395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:48:29.000Z","msg":"聽日幫手推"},{"pid":"221dca13782a9caed4b34bfe44e82c7b279ed863","tid":1288771,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad79991d996f18721b90a90b8ff5f869d202440","tid":1288771,"uid":50483,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T19:03:03.000Z","msg":"你可以係活動前/活動後做呢樣野<br />\n但咪撚係遊行期間去做<br />\n人地國際關注緊既係你香港 唔撚係中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你要支援武漢搞到個活動失焦 我真係多撚謝你"},{"pid":"e1d1dd41138928cdaa760f4e621466ecbe9b3239","tid":1288771,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T19:07:06.000Z","msg":"普通話：「你可以不支持我們，但你必須支持武漢的人民！政府壓迫他們，打他們，人民就必須反抗！」<br />\n<br />\n呢d火種傳入內地，先係共產黨最怕嘅事"},{"pid":"b3d02f73f98c2d6bb0f38593aeb3a20bb1eb3aad","tid":1288771,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike"